OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1772884978
OL,3,CMeghan Markle cuts ties with Netflix,
OL,4,Cas brand 'ready to stand on its own'
OL,6,FThe Duchess of Sussex has ended her
OL,7,Fjoint business venture with Netflix as
OL,8,Fshe felt the streaming giant was a bad
OL,9,Ffit for her homeware and lifestyle
OL,10,Fbrand, As ever.
OL,12,FMeghan announced a partnership with
OL,13,FNetflix a year ago when the streaming
OL,14,Fgiant commissioned a new season of her
OL,15,Fshow, 'With Love, Meghan'.
OL,17,FIt gave the media firm a stake in her
OL,18,FAs ever brand which includes jam, rose
OL,19,Fwine and flower sprinkles.
OL,26,@zD@frr
