OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1772884978
OL,3,CMeghan Markle cuts ties with Netflix,
OL,4,Cas brand 'ready to stand on its own'
OL,6,FITV News understands Meghan thought
OL,7,FNetflix was being too "cautious" with
OL,8,Fher growing range and she wanted to
OL,9,Fget new products to market more
OL,10,Fquickly.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FIt suggests that the reason for
OL,18,Fripping up the recently signed
OL,19,Fcontract was her idea rather than
OL,20,FNetflix's.
OL,26,@oD@WOUoD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
