OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1772884978
OL,3,CMeghan Markle cuts ties with Netflix,
OL,4,Cas brand 'ready to stand on its own'
OL,6,FIt contrasts with a decision by
OL,7,FSpotify, which decided to end its
OL,8,Fpartnership with the Sussexes and a
OL,9,Fformer boss of the music platform said
OL,10,Fsome very unkind things about Harry
OL,11,Fand Meghan in the weeks after the
OL,12,Fcontract was terminated.
OL,14,FA spokesperson for As ever said: "As
OL,15,Fever is grateful for Netflix's
OL,16,Fpartnership through launch and our
OL,17,Ffirst year. We have experienced
OL,18,Fmeaningful and rapid growth and As
OL,19,Fever is now ready to stand on its own.
OL,20,FWe have an exciting year ahead and
OL,21,Fcan't wait to share more."
OL,26,@vD@bOU}D@ZO]
