OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1772884978
OL,3,CMeghan Markle cuts ties with Netflix,
OL,4,Cas brand 'ready to stand on its own'
OL,6,FSome TV critics asked if it was an
OL,7,Fattempt by the Duchess to become a
OL,8,F'modern day Martha Stewart', the
OL,9,Ffamous American TV cook.
OL,11,FHarry and Meghan still have what's
OL,12,Fknown in the industry as a 'first
OL,13,Flook' deal with Netflix, which allows
OL,14,Fthe streamer to decide if it wants to
OL,15,Fcommission any of their ideas.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
