PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1772884978
OL,3,CMeghan Markle cuts ties with Netflix,
OL,4,Cas brand 'ready to stand on its own'
OL,6,FWhen the Duchess announced her new
OL,7,Fdeal with Netflix, she seemed
OL,8,Fdelighted to be partnering with them:
OL,9,F"Then Netflix came on, not just as my
OL,10,Fpartner in the show, but as my partner
OL,11,Fin my business, which was huge."
OL,13,FSources close to the Duchess said
OL,14,FNetflix were not very good at being "a
OL,15,Fshop" and are not set up "to sell
OL,16,Fproduct".
OL,18,FMeghan became frustrated with the slow
OL,19,Fgrowth of As Ever and has now decided
OL,20,Fto go it alone.
