OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1772884978
OL,3,CMeghan Markle cuts ties with Netflix,
OL,4,Cas brand 'ready to stand on its own'
OL,6,FNetflix said in a statement: "Meghan's
OL,7,Fpassion for elevating everyday moments
OL,8,Fin beautiful yet simple ways inspired
OL,9,Fthe creation of the As ever brand, and
OL,10,Fwe are glad to have played a role in
OL,11,Fbringing that vision to life.
OL,13,F"As it was always intended, Meghan
OL,14,Fwill continue growing the brand and
OL,15,Ftake it into its next chapter
OL,16,Findependently, and we look forward to
OL,17,Fcelebrating how she continues to bring
OL,18,Fjoy to households around the world."
